Daily Royal Events
2025 Daily Royal Events
Renaissance Romance Package
$60 Per Couple
Does not include festival admission
Romantic refreshments for two! Enjoy a front row view of the joust while being served a gourmet light lunch.
Your ticket includes two commemorative Renaissance Romance champagne flutes, light lunch, and one bottle of Moscato.
Non-alcoholic beverages available upon request. Must be 21 or older with valid ID to receive alcoholic beverages.
Daily at:
12:30 pm
2:30 pm
4:30 pm
BUY TICKETS NOW
Brunch at the Joust
$30 Per Person
Does not include festival admission
Enjoy a front row view of the Joust while being served a gourmet lunch.
Your ticket includes Brunch at the Joust commemorative glass, lunch, and one mimosa or non-alcoholic beverage.
Menu:
Smoked Turkey Leg with Creamy Classic Potato Salad, Buttermilk Cornbread, and a Freshly Baked Cookie.
All ages are welcome. Must be 21 or older with valid ID to receive a mimosa.
Seating is Community Table Style
Daily at:
12:30 pm
2:30 pm
4:30 pm
BUY TICKETS NOW
Mead-Evil Tastings
$45 Per Person
Does not include festival admission
Sample fine Meads! Your ticket includes 4 samples of Mead, Mead Tasting flask and Entertainment!
Hosted by Lorelei of Florida!
Must be 21+ with valid ID.
Daily at:
3:00 pm
BUY TICKETS NOW
Pub Crawl
$35 Per Person
Does not include festival admission
Follow our host on this popular beer tour across the realm. Drink thy beers, play good games, and keep your glass!
Your ticket includes 1 commemorative Pub Crawl glass and 1 drink at each of the three pubs.
Hosted by Cast of Folkstone!
Must be 21+ with valid ID to crawl!
Daily at:
12:30 pm
3:30 pm
BUY TICKETS NOW
Cocktail Crawl
$45 Per Person
Does not include festival admission
Enjoy a guided tour of our three cocktail bars! Enjoy bawdy entertainment along the way.
Your ticket includes one souvenir Cocktail Crawl glass and three cocktails.
Hosted by Cast of Folkstone!
Must be 21+ with valid ID to crawl!
Daily at:
2:00 pm
BUY TICKETS NOW
Queen’s Tea
$25 Per Person
Enjoy fine teas and delicious
hors d’oeuvres
while being regaled with song and stories!
Visit with the Royal Court. Receive a commemorative Queen’s Tea glass and collectible pin.
Hosted by Cast of Folkstone!
Saturdays at:
1:00 pm
BUY TICKETS NOW
Fairy Tale Tea Party
$25 Per Person
Does not include festival admission
Mingle with the Fairies while crafting your own edible fairy garden, join in whimsical activities and capture magical memories.
Your ticket includes one edible fairy garden and a commemorative Fairytale Tea Party tea glass.
For Children ages 4-11 years. Parents must accompany children. Parents do not need to purchase a ticket.
Hosted by The Fae!
Daily at:
12:00 pm
BUY TICKETS NOW

Welcome to the 2025 Bay Area Renaissance Festival!
The Bay Area Renaissance Festival is celebrating its 47th season!
Come and be a part of this long-standing tradition by visiting the festival grounds in Dade City, FL.
WEEKENDS FEBRUARY 15TH – MARCH 30TH
INCLUDING LADIES AND LORDS SHOPPING DAY ON MARCH 9TH
10AM – 6PM
RAIN OR SHINE!

About the Bay Area Renaissance Festival
Since its debut in Largo, Florida, the Bay Area Renaissance Festival has grown into one of Florida’s most beloved annual traditions. Set in the heart of Dade City, our vibrant festival invites guests to step into a 16th-century European village with 15 stages of entertainment, over 100 talented artisans, and immersive historical experiences. As we celebrate our 47th season, we welcome families, history buffs, and adventure seekers to experience an unforgettable world of fun, feasts, and festivities for all ages!
For more information about Mid-America Festivals
visit our website!
